{"tid":1563473,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"多蒙特確認曼聯斟介：但辛祖唔想入魔","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:25:19.000Z","uid":59732,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"433105ab139368f41b69185c22fbac3cef297be3","tid":1563473,"uid":59732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/bd/1e/jadon-sancho-borussia-dortmund-2019-20_f2503etmufvz1mk2hwonwe65s.jpg?t=1908496108&amp;quality=60&amp;w=1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2Fbd%2F1e%2Fjadon-sancho-borussia-dortmund-2019-20_f2503etmufvz1mk2hwonwe65s.jpg%3Ft%3D1908496108%26quality%3D60%26w%3D1600&h=689838c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多蒙特體育總監米高素歷表示，曼聯於今夏的確向「蜜蜂兵團」查詢查頓辛祖，是否有機會過檔奧脫福，但多蒙特明確表示辛祖是非賣品；另外他亦強調，辛祖亦沒有意思加盟曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n辛祖於17年8月以900萬鎊，由曼城轉會多蒙特，之後於上季大爆發，34次上陣貢獻12個入球及14次助攻，帶領球隊嚴重威脅拜仁德甲王朝。他亦成功入選英格蘭國家隊，故惹來曼聯興趣。<br />\n<br />\n米高素歷道：「辛祖對多蒙特好重要，而曼聯確實對他有興趣。今夏曼聯正式和多蒙特展開傾談，但我們明確地向紅魔鬼表示，無論任何價錢都不會讓辛祖轉會。另外以我所知，辛祖亦希望留隊，對轉會曼聯毫無興趣。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=b9a365be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"0b40bfbfa72e4f52b87cd7bcb6bc906a4d051ce4","tid":1563473,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f353446b96a7a7af5006171d733fe739eb3520cd","tid":1563473,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾獌"},{"pid":"7af7c4b42cd050d3274084b02a8f2773698e4683","tid":1563473,"uid":45505,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"係辛祖嘅損失"},{"pid":"145af359e93c6f4433945f1d8d7d4f332a6e232b","tid":1563473,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"我大曼聯帝國唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef130d6bc51935f7db2416b69bf68d61323a04e","tid":1563473,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"曼聯唯一希望係突然有勁青訓<br />\n打起成隊波<br />\n吸引番人地黎<br />\n早幾年有錢有名氣唔買人<br />\n依家有錢人地都唔肯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65ff1086f3fe3be4dbfe936d0e8bf249d760128","tid":1563473,"uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"也許辛祖的想法是，我想要踢歐聯比賽，否則我寧願坐在後備席上。我願意當後備，也不想給曼聯踢比賽。好吧。其實辛祖沒來曼聯，我還挺高興的，因為他身上沒有一丁點曼聯需要的品質。"},{"pid":"4e2afa95f965e646239980d0c405d92a73dde19d","tid":1563473,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b65ff1086f3fe3be4dbfe936d0e8bf249d760128","tid":1563473,"uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"也許辛祖的想法是，我想要踢歐聯比賽，否則我寧願坐在後備席上。我願意當後備，也不想給曼聯踢比賽。好吧。其實辛祖沒來曼聯，我還挺高興的，因為他身上沒有一丁點曼聯需要的品質。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"酸撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b1b5e0a541b9439923e42beafa409c3195a89e","tid":1563473,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ef130d6bc51935f7db